'''Bridge Alliance''' （原'''Bridge Mobile Alliance'''）是一個國際商業聯盟，[[亞太地區|亞太地區]]最大[[行動通訊|行動通訊]]聯盟，由36個各大電信營運商公司在[[亞洲|亞洲]]、[[澳洲|澳洲]]、[[非洲|非洲]]和[[中東|中東]]地區建立聯盟在國際間無縫連接的[[漫遊|漫遊]]服務和提供方便且合理優惠的[[語音|語音]][[數據|數據]]漫遊服務，使所有聯盟成員的用戶，都能漫遊對方的網絡；並促進會員間產品和商業策略的合作平台。

目前，Bridge Alliance成員在全球34個市場中擁有超過8億用戶。

Bridge Alliance的合作夥伴包括[[AT&T|AT&T]]、[[中國聯通|中國聯通]]、[[全球M2M協會|全球M2M協會]]。同時與在歐洲[[FreeMove|FreeMove]]聯盟有合作關係。<ref name="partnership">[http://www.bridgealliance.com/news/news_270307.html FreeMove and Bridge Mobile Alliance to establish alliance-to-alliance cooperation] {{Wayback|url=http://www.bridgealliance.com/news/news_270307.html |date=20081022060019 }}, Bridge Mobile Press Release, March 27, 2007</ref>

==歷史==
'''2004年'''
*七家領先的亞太移動運營商組成了該地區最大的合資移動公司。<ref>"[http://wirelesswatch.jp/2004/11/04/telcos-form-bridge-mobile-alliance/ Telcos Form Bridge Mobile Alliance] {{Wayback|url=http://wirelesswatch.jp/2004/11/04/telcos-form-bridge-mobile-alliance/ |date=20191227152250 }}". Wireless Watch Japan. 4 November 2004.</ref>

'''2005年'''
*Bridge和[[SingTel|SingTel]]發起了他們的首個區域移動通訊合作。<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.bridgealliance.com/news-details.aspx?id=14Sep2005&t=B2010 |title=Battle for Asia’s 1st World Cyber Games Mobile champs |date=14 September 2005 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130526050307/http://www.bridgealliance.com/news-details.aspx?id=14Sep2005&t=B2010 |archivedate=2013-05-26 |accessdate=2019-12-27 |dead-url=no }}</ref>
*[[CSL|CSL]]加入了Bridge Alliance。<ref>"[http://www.totaltele.com/view.aspx?ID=367128 Asia's Bridge Mobile Alliance launches services, adds HK CSL] {{Wayback|url=http://www.totaltele.com/view.aspx?ID=367128 |date=20200729160202 }}". Total Telecom. 13 June 2005.</ref>

'''2006年'''
*Bridge Alliance歡迎[[CTM|CTM]]作為其最新的運營商成員。<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.bridgealliance.com/news-details.aspx?id=27Nov2006&t=B2010 |title=Bridge Mobile Alliance welcomes CTM as its newest operator member |date=27 November 2006 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130526044930/http://www.bridgealliance.com/news-details.aspx?id=27Nov2006&t=B2010 |archivedate=2013-05-26 |accessdate=2019-12-27 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

'''2007年'''
*Bridge Alliance推出了上限計劃，在11個地區提供統一的數據漫遊費率。<ref>"[http://info.singtel.com/node/3034 Asia Pacific's leading Bridge Alliance launches one-flat data] {{Wayback|url=http://info.singtel.com/node/3034 |date=20160303233549 }}". SingTel. 5 November 2007.</ref>
*FreeMove與Bridge Alliance建立了合作夥伴關係。<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.bridgealliance.com/news-details.aspx?id=27Mar2007&t=B2010 |title=FreeMove and Bridge Mobile Alliance to establish alliance-to-alliance cooperation |date=27 March 2007 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130526043810/http://www.bridgealliance.com/news-details.aspx?id=27Mar2007&t=B2010 |archivedate=2013-05-26 |accessdate=2019-12-27 |dead-url=no }}</ref>
*增加了兩個新成員：[[SK電訊|SK電訊]]和[[AIS|AIS]]。<ref>"[https://archive.today/20130830191438/http://www.skroaming.com/en/customer/notice_view.asp?idx=164&cPage=3&search_data=&select_value= SK Telecom, expands 3G global alliance]". SK Telecom. 9 March 2007.</ref><ref>"[https://archive.is/20130830191459/http://info.singtel.com/node/2953 Bridge Mobile Alliance welcomes Advanced Info Service as its 11th operator member]". SingTel. 18 June 2007.</ref>

'''2010年'''
*Bridge Alliance在所有聯盟成員國中推出了統一費率的每日無限制數據漫遊計劃。<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.bridgealliance.com/news-details.aspx?id=01Nov2010&t=2010 |title=Bridge Alliance launches one-flat rate, daily unlimited data roaming plan across 11 territories |date=1 November 2010 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130526025136/http://www.bridgealliance.com/news-details.aspx?id=01Nov2010&t=2010 |archivedate=2013-05-26 |accessdate=2019-12-27 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

'''2011年'''
*AIS和Globe為整個亞太地區提供Bridge VoiceSMS漫遊，一費率語音和SMS漫遊價格計劃。<ref>"[https://archive.today/20130830191444/http://asia.etbnews.com/41775/globe-telecom-offers-cost-savings-for-customers-with-bridge-voicesms-roam/ Globe Telecom Offers Cost Savings for Customers With Bridge VoiceSMS Roam]". ETB News. 14 December 2011.</ref>
*Bridge AsiaRoamData SIM服務已擴展到11個國家/地區。<ref>"[http://www.cellular-news.com/story/51838.php Bridge Alliance Expands Fixed Fee Mobile Data Roaming to 11 Countries] {{Wayback|url=http://www.cellular-news.com/story/51838.php |date=20111117224120 }}". Cellular-news. 16 November 2011.</ref>

'''2012年'''
*Bridge Alliance擴展到越南，並歡迎[[MobiFone|MobiFone]]成為其第12個成員。<ref>"[http://www.cellular-news.com/story/57941.php 12 Short Stories About the Mobile Networks] {{Wayback|url=http://www.cellular-news.com/story/57941.php |date=20130116130036 }}". Cellular-news. 27 December 2012.</ref>
*Bridge Alliance和[[Softbank_Mobile|Softbank Mobile]]建立了業務合作夥伴關係，以擴展其企業產品。<ref>"[http://www.itwire.com/it-industry-news/strategy/52076-bridge-alliance-teams-with-softbank-to-target-multinationals Bridge Alliance teams with Softbank to target multinationals] {{Wayback|url=http://www.itwire.com/it-industry-news/strategy/52076-bridge-alliance-teams-with-softbank-to-target-multinationals |date=20191227213943 }}". IT Wire. 10 January 2012.</ref>

'''2013年'''
*非洲[[Airtel|Airtel]]加入Bridge Alliance。
*孟加拉[[Airtel|Airtel]]加入Bridge Alliance。
*[[Telkomcel|Telkomcel]]加入Bridge Alliance成為其第13個成員。

'''2014年'''
*[[STC|STC]]加入Bridge Alliance。
*Softbank Mobile加入Bridge Alliance。

'''2016年'''
*Bridge Alliance和全球M2M協會合作推動M2M和物聯網市場的全球增長。<ref>{{cite web|title=bridgealliance|url=http://www.bridgealliance.com/|website=www.bridgealliance.com|accessdate=2016-01-22|archive-date=2016-01-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160124190804/http://www.bridgealliance.com/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

'''2017年'''
*Bridge Alliance和FreeMove擴展了合作夥伴關係，以在106個市場中提供集成的企業移動性。<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.bridgealliance.com/2017/06/19/bridge-alliance-freemove-extend-partnership-offer-integrated-enterprise-mobility-across-106-markets/|title=Bridge Alliance and FreeMove extend partnership to offer integrated Enterprise Mobility across 106 markets|date=2017-06-19|work=Bridge Alliance|access-date=2017-10-02|language=en-US|archive-date=2017-10-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171002120521/http://www.bridgealliance.com/2017/06/19/bridge-alliance-freemove-extend-partnership-offer-integrated-enterprise-mobility-across-106-markets/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

